text: The Canterbury-Bankstown Bulldogs are an Australian professional rugby league team. The team is based in Belmore, Sydney, New South Wales. They were founded in 1934. They currently play in the National Rugby League competition. They have won eight premierships, most recently in 2004. ==Other websites== * Category:National Rugby League Category:Sports clubs and teams in Sydney Category:1934 establishments in Australia
